post.body: People who bite the hand that feeds them usually lick the boot that kicks them.
I am furious to my core at what has been done to gay culture. It used to save people. Now it enslaves them.
The only question right now is, will this last or will people prefer the enslavement machine by the pedo-elites?
Little annoying: it's kind of slow, still acceptable though. How will it behave when it grows into something? Does anyone know?
Can I execute PHP or other binaries on zeronet? Anyone knows?
I know Bitcoin will be something, I hope zeronet (or something else very similar) can also be.
Do you know what the Holocaust is? 9 gay guys died in a rollerblading accident. Holocaust denial is a crime. We must never forget how tragically those 9 gay guys died.
